LINK: https://platform.stratascratch.com/coding/10049-reviews-of-categories?code_type=5

==> My approach:
WITH SplitCategory AS (
SELECT *
     , value AS category
FROM yelp_business
CROSS APPLY 
     STRING_SPLIT(categories, ';')
)
SELECT category
     , SUM(review_count) AS review_cnt
FROM SplitCategory
GROUP BY category
ORDER BY review_cnt DESC;

